<p>Check out the names of them all and how to add them to your collection—credit to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.truetrophies.com/news/mafia-the-old-country-playstation-trophies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">TrueTrophies</a>.</p>



