<h2 id="h-how-many-trophies-amp-achievements-in-mafia-the-old-country">How Many Trophies &amp; Achievements in Mafia: The Old Country? </h2>



<p><strong>There are 25 normal and 26 secret trophies and achievements in Mafia: The Old Country.</strong></p>



<p>Completing a playthrough on hard difficulty will earn most trophies and achievements, without having to go too much out of your way. However, there are a few trophies in particular that require skill and patience, such as killing Mazzone without alerting his men and infiltrating the villa without being seen. </p>



<p>Do you plan on earning every trophy? Let us know on the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum/threads/complete-mafia-the-old-country-trophy-list-how-to-get-all-achievements-and-trophies.3223/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Insider Gaming Forum</a>. </p>



